<p>A three column CSS grid. The first two grid columns are fixed at 150px.  The third grid column hase a minimum width of 150px and a maximum of 1fr defined using minmax() notation.</p>

<p>
  <div class="wrapper3ColFluidRight">
    <div class="box a">A</div>
    <div class="box b">B</div>
    <div class="box c">C</div>
  </div>
</p>

<p>
  The above CSS grid layout applied to an input-group with an addon:</p>  
<p>

<p> 
  <div class="input-group wrapper3ColFluidRight">
    <span class="form-control input-group-addon">Add On</span>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="field one">
    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="field two">
  </div>
</p> 